919a6990-3a89-4435-87b7-5590e3c0aba5	8589c927-3407-4699-a382-d6df6a045d8b	64	<chunk_context>Lời mời tư vấn và chào mời quà tặng cho khách hàng mới tại Dr. Medispa, kết thúc phần giới thiệu dịch vụ chăm sóc da hoặc điều trị cụ thể.</chunk_context>\n\nKhông biết chị cần em tư vấn hoặc giải đáp thêm gì về dịch vụ [thay tên dịch vụ] không ạ? Hiện tại bên em đang có nhiều quà tặng đặc biệt cho khách hàng mới, em mời chị sắp xếp thời gian qua spa chăm sóc và thư giãn nhé ạ!",	< chunk_context > Lời mời tư_vấn và chào_mời quà tặng cho khách_hàng mới tại Dr._Medispa , kết_thúc phần giới_thiệu dịch_vụ chăm_sóc da hoặc điều_trị cụ_thể . < / chunk_context > Không biết chị cần em tư_vấn hoặc giải_đáp thêm gì về dịch_vụ [ thay tên dịch_vụ ] không ạ ? Hiện_tại bên em đang có nhiều quà tặng đặc_biệt cho khách_hàng mới , em mời chị sắp_xếp thời_gian qua spa chăm_sóc và thư_giãn nhé ạ ! " ,	f7bc446f2368fd72fea887dbdcda4eefc0b2f308645180f3ae35b8a3613e1a5c	[0.02228645,0.02985936,0.1252086,0.0496581,0.07337867,-0.04736244,0.030526,0.08236486,0.10700899,-0.03285059,-0.01535129,0.08955281,0.09309923,-0.01217036,-0.04521752,-0.03450137,-0.01757963,0.03222256,0.07905871,0.0771471,-0.15364951,-0.01921929,-0.07402343,-0.03306974,-0.02353178,-0.09261651,0.05244558,-0.00390205,-0.0560184,-0.03363785,-0.00402619,-0.0785721,-0.04645698,0.06769158,0.09655192,-0.05614369,-0.02327546,-0.0139119,0.01267978,-0.01921847,-0.10330831,0.03562543,0.06943825,0.05188829,0.00427945,0.03607338,-0.0309628,-0.01309879,0.10566438,-0.00475673,-0.05844406,0.02537199,0.02404609,0.00502329,-0.00262135,0.0565387,-0.02037854,-0.01326911,0.07938451,-0.02988126,-0.03269456,0.02482074,0.01586514,0.03655184,0.00987368,0.02229264,-0.05629669,0.0373054,0.01169291,-0.03755075,0.0546576,0.05121818,-0.00023416,0.10848305,0.02325724,-0.00652522,3.676e-05,0.05086247,-0.09875149,-0.04818409,-0.05765272,0.05786091,-9.519e-05,-0.02070269,0.00256285,-0.05549259,0.04815898,0.03201269,0.11962076,-0.00441887,-0.00745767,-0.02881834,-0.0