a5d40282-42d6-457a-9ac6-6f434899116d	8589c927-3407-4699-a382-d6df6a045d8b	69	<chunk_context>Kết thúc tư vấn dịch vụ tại Dr. Medispa, mời khách đặt lịch trải nghiệm và nhận quà tặng khách hàng mới</chunk_context>\n\nKhông biết chị cần em tư vấn hoặc giải đáp thêm gì về dịch vụ [thay tên dịch vụ] không ạ? Hiện tại bên em đang có nhiều quà tặng đặc biệt cho khách hàng mới, em mời chị sắp xếp thời gian qua spa chăm sóc và thư giãn nhé ạ!",	< chunk_context > Kết_thúc tư_vấn dịch_vụ tại Dr._Medispa , mời khách đặt lịch trải_nghiệm và nhận quà tặng khách_hàng mới < / chunk_context > Không biết chị cần em tư_vấn hoặc giải_đáp thêm gì về dịch_vụ [ thay tên dịch_vụ ] không ạ ? Hiện_tại bên em đang có nhiều quà tặng đặc_biệt cho khách_hàng mới , em mời chị sắp_xếp thời_gian qua spa chăm_sóc và thư_giãn nhé ạ ! " ,	f11945e0ff88b27a10f39f19faf5f453adab84e9b24e2b1622d3776fac1da742	[0.02632185,0.03193508,0.12876351,0.06138095,0.08588617,-0.04091021,0.02384079,0.09548847,0.10230863,-0.04545748,-0.01566186,0.06636098,0.10636509,-0.0127817,-0.04872463,-0.03683054,0.00047757,0.03067084,0.05618841,0.09066059,-0.15132658,-0.02436339,-0.08036675,-0.03405755,-0.02456751,-0.10183675,0.05370846,0.01971702,-0.05856107,-0.02874728,0.0123683,-0.07992896,-0.04671002,0.07365917,0.09269419,-0.05044348,-0.01766432,-0.03342705,0.01700201,-0.00973882,-0.09718613,0.03116759,0.06896905,0.05705395,-0.00356452,0.03423904,-0.0353411,-0.00800109,0.09050176,-0.00605494,-0.04223382,0.03844431,0.03934197,0.00225244,-0.01441127,0.06285705,-0.0235687,0.01453422,0.06784744,-0.02511407,-0.0246368,0.02588934,0.02621047,0.02149436,0.00649712,0.01689741,-0.04334572,0.04516179,0.02119141,-0.04580851,0.06438421,0.06588178,0.00163854,0.11781192,0.0271465,-0.00561675,-0.00472642,0.05359521,-0.08983987,-0.04514366,-0.06368403,0.0525026,0.01079854,-0.02582542,0.00611623,-0.06153747,0.05630692,0.03432341,0.10878349,-0.01114422,-0.0058437,-0.04928484,-0.02760788,-0.01939717,0.08878443,0.01415249,-0.11010943,0.07097149,0.00