9434443f-17a6-4a00-ac4f-a65a5f008b51	8589c927-3407-4699-a382-d6df6a045d8b	150	<chunk_context>Ưu đãi dịch vụ massage chân tại Dr. Medispa dành cho khách hàng mới, giá 99K/buổi (gốc 350K), thời gian 70 phút.</chunk_context>\n\nHiện tại, bên em đang có chương trình ưu đãi đặc biệt cho khách hàng mới trải nghiệm dịch vụ với giá chỉ 99K/buổi (giá gốc: 350k/buổi) trong vòng 70 phút. Sau 1 buổi chị sẽ cảm thấy cơ thể khỏe khoắn, đỡ mỏi mệt hơn hẳn ạ.	< chunk_context > Ưu_đãi dịch_vụ massage chân tại Dr._Medispa dành cho khách_hàng mới , giá 99K / buổi ( gốc 350K ) , thời_gian 70 phút . < / chunk_context > Hiện_tại , bên em đang có chương_trình ưu_đãi đặc_biệt cho khách_hàng mới trải_nghiệm dịch_vụ với giá chỉ 99K / buổi ( giá gốc : 350 k / buổi ) trong vòng 70 phút . Sau 1 buổi chị sẽ cảm_thấy cơ_thể khỏe khoắn , đỡ mỏi_mệt hơn hẳn ạ .	58a927caba06cca2b7f5e4e99e4a194f84270027a2c1b5e220f9544f3d203f11	[0.01423333,0.02193226,0.08597375,0.08688398,0.07654173,0.00246753,-0.01959218,0.11122893,0.0865972,-0.03503198,0.00586323,0.05030894,0.09613079,-0.00618507,-0.03258171,-0.04324826,0.03555228,0.02156035,0.06018322,0.08915491,-0.17038381,0.00185563,-0.03127213,-0.01872839,0.02653982,-0.11471613,0.05459857,0.00770815,-0.08160959,-0.02963409,-0.00019007,-0.04243604,-0.03142048,0.10491926,0.08801014,-0.0257469,-0.01944142,-0.04672471,-0.01924982,0.00794431,-0.06852686,0.00467493,0.05066492,0.04953827,0.05345701,-0.01393482,-0.02819372,-0.07525922,0.11066274,-0.02331208,-0.06083889,0.00138655,0.00579995,0.01671616,-0.01825175,0.03104343,-0.01902371,0.00223842,0.08730184,-0.03802213,-0.03949474,0.05460116,-0.02324201,0.01209795,0.00961009,0.00572796,-0.02654481,0.05461322,0.02055822,-0.04823228,0.06323219,0.03972534,0.01134825,0.1302746,0.04499035,0.04844966,-0.00705059,0.05171576,-0.05496023,-0.04185302,-0.04030029,0.01781199,-0.02416982,0.00694583,-0.00524965,-0.04003611,0.05784138,0.03074646,0.11474226,0.01091254,-0.00932162,-0.04236788,-0.01976384,0.00383597,0.08286626,0.00713981