def6865e-0e82-4996-8769-4a40f15af302	8589c927-3407-4699-a382-d6df6a045d8b	175	<chunk_context>Ưu đãi dịch vụ ấm nóng cổ tử cung và thải độc bi tại Dr. Medispa cho khách hàng mới, giá ưu đãi 499K/buổi (gốc 3000K), thời gian 120 phút, hiệu quả thư giãn.</chunk_context>\n\nHiện tại, bên em đang có chương trình ưu đãi đặc biệt cho khách hàng mới trải nghiệm dịch vụ với giá chỉ 499K/buổi (giá gốc: 3000k/buổi) trong vòng 120 phút. Sau 1 buổi chị sẽ cảm thấy thư giãn dễ chịu hơn rất nhiều ạ.	< chunk_context > Ưu_đãi dịch_vụ ấm nóng cổ_tử_cung và thải độc_bi tại Dr._Medispa cho khách_hàng mới , giá ưu_đãi 499K / buổi ( gốc 3000K ) , thời_gian 120 phút , hiệu_quả thư_giãn . < / chunk_context > Hiện_tại , bên em đang có chương_trình ưu_đãi đặc_biệt cho khách_hàng mới trải_nghiệm dịch_vụ với giá chỉ 499K / buổi ( giá gốc : 3000 k / buổi ) trong vòng 120 phút . Sau 1 buổi chị sẽ cảm_thấy thư_giãn dễ_chịu hơn rất nhiều ạ .	1245fb9607e89c34bf849afe5bff5d48b888f4079685c4d304c9c0275883d081	[0.02946068,0.07132813,0.06560423,0.08374006,0.09962326,-0.07073179,0.00254463,0.09205356,0.06695993,0.01309079,-0.00721734,0.06945762,0.08311035,-0.0010114,-0.07892629,-0.071383,-0.00175527,0.06211952,0.0269409,0.06818493,-0.12607677,-0.02351639,-0.08279148,-0.00642532,-0.02098101,-0.08715536,0.06671478,0.04505938,-0.09744568,-0.04492459,-0.00644905,-0.0487961,0.00498501,0.10615712,0.11712836,-0.07042228,-0.01024022,-0.02643461,-0.00603003,0.00829626,-0.06551468,0.02284058,0.07257753,0.03718049,0.05024277,0.01763182,-0.04695907,-0.00835268,0.08606946,0.01241021,-0.01618139,0.00218256,-0.02465378,0.01079674,-0.04281924,0.06803425,0.00666684,-0.01767867,0.06165454,0.00033822,0.00349853,-0.00708474,-0.00321857,0.03636569,-0.04789342,0.03303636,-0.02716102,0.01536084,0.04964568,-0.0744331,0.05972023,0.01229424,-0.0034224,0.09775843,0.05486196,0.03124674,0.01090609,0.02681122,-0.06230502,-0.03447436,-0.01018813,0.05544683,0.00160979,-0.01753463,0.02552078,-0.05159879,0.00494072,0.08296855,0.09165618,-