73a7ccba-e4c5-4d71-aa9f-d448a84e94c8	8589c927-3407-4699-a382-d6df6a045d8b	178	<chunk_context>Dịch vụ chuyển hóa bụng tại Dr. Medispa, tư vấn và đặt lịch chăm sóc vùng bụng thon gọn, săn chắc, thải độc nội tạng, lưu thông khí huyết.</chunk_context>\n\n,Chuyển hóa bụng,"Dạ, dịch vụ chuyển hóa bụng bên em được thực hiện bởi chuyên viên kinh nghiệm, giúp vùng bụng thon gọn, săn chắc hơn hơn, hỗ trợ thải độc nội tạng, lưu thông khí huyết. Em hỗ trợ chị đặt lịch trải nghiệm dịch vụ nhé ạ?	< chunk_context > Dịch_vụ chuyển hóa bụng tại Dr._Medispa , tư_vấn và đặt lịch chăm_sóc vùng bụng thon gọn , săn chắc , thải độc nội_tạng , lưu_thông khí_huyết . < / chunk_context > , Chuyển hóa bụng , " Dạ , dịch_vụ chuyển hóa bụng bên em được thực_hiện bởi chuyên_viên kinh_nghiệm , giúp vùng bụng thon gọn , săn chắc hơn hơn , hỗ_trợ thải độc nội_tạng , lưu_thông khí_huyết . Em hỗ_trợ chị đặt lịch trải_nghiệm dịch_vụ nhé ạ ?	85a455e38a3ab159fcbc5c648d59a31a22e379698c4ba934d0b7926cb0c2b7d3	[0.05547094,0.02010982,0.09892032,0.08663456,0.02585931,-0.00356835,0.00798756,0.07350992,0.07758641,-0.00650135,-0.07248456,0.11173888,0.04266593,-0.06134973,-0.04362798,-0.036697,0.01533485,0.03278385,0.06389941,0.11503919,-0.13629757,-0.03405454,-0.06833313,-0.01872809,-0.00160198,-0.05848998,0.06141835,0.02693336,-0.0756912,-0.07887597,0.02253036,-0.04106737,-0.01022523,0.0568788,0.0626397,-0.03425714,-0.02879772,-0.02609949,-0.00096172,-0.0154668,-0.06510545,0.0164012,0.02899783,0.02223137,-0.00387178,-0.03380714,-0.03991166,0.00662461,0.11614783,0.02415489,0.0274146,0.02843046,0.00213359,0.04291464,-0.03329217,0.01413142,-0.03772359,-0.04144068,0.05436247,0.02659115,0.00507033,0.03473254,0.0038627,0.04257377,-0.01396582,0.0359229,0.02605802,0.01934783,0.05599842,-0.0799863,0.04211208,0.06506165,0.04606627,0.09029103,-0.00428937,0.01049942,0.00857768,0.02355725,-0.03108948,0.0006362,-0.08352907,0.05836724,-0.03166543,-0.07920098,0.03395637,-0.07878274,0.01002966,0.06807099,0.0928668,0.01034827,0.0